      • evaluate

        public boolean evaluate​(Polyad polyad,
                        State state)
        Description copied from class: AbstractEvaluator
        Decides if a Polyad is evaluated by this evaluator and if not, returns false, if so, it evaluates it and returns true. This function actually just dispatches it to AbstractEvaluator.dispatch(Polyad, State) where the work is done and manages putting better trace information in if there is a failure.
